#!/bin/bash
YELLOW='\033[1;33m'
NC='\033[0m'
echo -e "${YELLOW}系統概況 (System Overview)${NC}"
if [[ "$(uname)" == "Darwin" ]]; then
    echo "- OS: $(sw_vers -productName) $(sw_vers -productVersion) ($(uname -m))"
else
    OS_NAME=$(lsb_release -ds 2>/dev/null || cat /etc/os-release | grep PRETTY_NAME | cut -d'"' -f2 || uname -sr)
    echo "- OS: $OS_NAME"
fi
echo "- Date: $(date)"
